list.title: ui5-cc-dndashboard.Dashboard
list.description:
Constructor for a new Dashboard control.

Overview

The ui5-cc-dndashboard.Dashboard is a container control that holds the dashboard . The Dashboard accepts aggregation tiles of type ui5-cc-dndashboard.DashboardTile which is the draggable component.
